org.apache.hadoop.hbase

Class ClusterStatus.Options

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.ClusterStatus.Options
  • Enclosing class:
    ClusterStatus

    public static class ClusterStatus.Options
extends Object
    Options provides a way to filter out unwanted information. For compatibility, default options includes all the information about a ClusterStatus. To filter out unwanted information, use the specific excludeXXX() method.
